query:
INSERT INTO question_submission (
                    id,
                    question_id,
                    respondent_id,
                    response,
                    sentiment
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5
                ) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                    response = $4,
                    sentiment = $5,
                    updated_at = now()
                RETURNING 
                    id,
                    question_id,
                    respondent_id,
                    response,
                    sentiment AS "sentiment:Sentiment",
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
